        "title": "Core Concepts of AWS",
        "content": "Understand the foundational elements of AWS, including:\n- Cloud Computing: Delivery of computing services over the internet.\n- AWS Services: A wide range of services including computing power, storage, and databases."
      },
      {
        "title": "Regions and Availability Zones",
        "content": "Learn about the geographical distribution of AWS resources:\n- Regions: Isolated geographical areas.\n- Availability Zones: Multiple data centers within a region to ensure high availability."
      },
      {
        "title": "Key Resources for Learning AWS",
        "content": "Utilize various resources to enhance your understanding:\n- Flashcards: Quick definitions of key terms like Cloud Computing and AWS Services.\n- Videos: Engaging tutorials such as 'AWS In 5 Minutes' for a brief overview."
      }
    ]
  }
}
